These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, time-travel
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, drawing
City: colone, hamburg
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel    | comedy |
| Hobby         | drawing | chess    |
| City     | colone     | hamburg      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
City: venice, liverpool
There 2 different types of food: mango, banana
House: tower, wooden
1. the wooden house is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
2. the person eating mango is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| City      | liverpool  | venice   |
| Food   | banana | mango  |
| House     | wooden   | tower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different pets are kept: lizard, frog
House: farmhouse, art-deco
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, folk
1. the owner of the frog is in an even position##4
2. the farmhouse house is on the right of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Pet         | lizard   | frog  |
| House   | art-deco | farmhouse  |
| Music-Genre         | punk   | folk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, firefighter
House: gothic-revival, wooden
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, marigold
1. the person who growstulip is on the right of the wooden house##1
2. the chef is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Job          | chef | firefighter |
| House   | wooden   | gothic-revival   |
| Flower     | marigold       | tulip      |

