The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, adventure
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, october
1. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |
