.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There are 2 different nationalities: american, pakistani
The people have 2 different hobbies: writing, collecting
House: gothic-revival, craftsman
1. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
3. the american is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Nationality    | pakistani | american     |
| Hobby     | collecting | writing |
| House   | craftsman | gothic-revival    |

