.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
House: modern, farmhouse
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, scientific
2 different games are played: monopoly, canasta
1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the modern house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| House         | farmhouse | modern |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | scientific     |
| Game           | canasta          | monopoly     |

